query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math') AND t1.name IN ('banach-spaces',
'complex-integration',
'computational-complexity',
'contest-math',
'distribution-theory',
'galois-theory',
'maxima-minima',
'operator-algebras',
'real-numbers',
'supremum-and-infimum')
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Benefactor',
'Cleanup',
'Fanatic',
'Good Question',
'Mortarboard',
'Necromancer')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
